name: Peek-a-Boo
description: It was back in 2013 when I took this picture. This little girl was very curious of what I'm doing in her neighborhood. She's a very shy girl. I remember she always hide when I point my camera to her, so I let her peek me and I took this photo. It's a split second moment between me and the shutter button either I took it or it'll gone forever. That's a beautiful moment to remember for me.
